name: 威廉·奥利弗
introduction: William Isaiah "Will" Oliver is an American actor born and raised in Columbus, Georgia, USA. He is the son of Timothy and Debbie Oliver. Will attended Northside High School, where he soon began to captivate the audience with his stage presence. After high school, he would then further his education at Columbus State University to enhance his craft.
